SMOK Vape Kit
Vaping.com has the perfect refillable vape pod kit for disposable vape users. If you are an adult looking for a more eco-friendly way to enjoy salt nicotine vape juices, the sturdy, reliable and flavorful Smok Novo 3 is a perfect choice.
The draw-activated Smok Novo 3 is powered by an 800mAh battery and generates up to 25 watts of power. It has a very compact size. It is compatible with original Novo, Novo 2, Novo 2X and of course Novo 3 pods. Each pod holds 2ml of e-liquid, and this vape pod kit comes with a pair of 0.8ohm Novo 3 pods. The pods use an integrated coil design which requires no swapping of coils and reduces the threat of leakage.
The Smok Novo 3 is a perfect alternative to disposable vapes and excels at extracting flavor from nicotine salts. But the lower resistance pods also work great with regular e-liquids. This was the perfected pod design right out of the gates and a worthy device for novice and veteran vapers alike.

description:
SMOK Vape Kit
Vaping.com carries the flagship of the Smok Novo line-up. The Smok Novo 4 is a 25-watt refillable vape pod kit. It retains the compact form factor and functionality of the original Novo but adds useful features like adjustable wattage and airflow.
Coils are no longer integrated but can be swapped out. This makes it an eco-friendlier alternative to disposable vapes, as only the coil needs replacing. It also features a 0.49" OLED Screen, which allows for adjustable wattage control. It operates between 5 and 25-watts.
It uses the LP1 coil family, featuring three resistance choices, have improved leak-reducing technology. Powered by an 800mAh battery, the Smok Novo 4 is optimized for discrete and flavorful vaping.
With a 2ml capacity, the Smok Novo 4 is an efficient device that extracts every bit of flavor from nic salts but has the power to handle regular freebase e-liquids as well. Each Smok Novo 4 kit includes the Novo 4 device, two 0.8ohm mesh coils, one 2ml Novo 4 pod, and a USB-C cable.

description:
SMOK NOVO Pro Kit Refillable Pod Vape

The Smok Novo Pro retains the classic shape and compact size of its predecessor, the Smok Novo, but boasts an enhanced design with a screen and backward compatibility with Novo, Novo 2, Novo 2X, and Novo 3 pod designs. Adult vapor consumers can rely on its impeccable flavor that is geared for nicotine salt delivery, making it a top choice for veterans and novices alike.
The Smok Novo Pro Kit features a 1300mAh battery and delivers an impressive 30-watts of power. As a compact and slim pod kit, it is the perfect choice for nic salt vapers who are looking for a more eco-friendly alternative to disposable vapes. With its professional grade design, there is no better option for those ready to switch to a greener vaping experience.
The 0.42" OLED display offers customizable wattage settings. The airflow can be easily adjusted using a simple switch. Additionally, the device offers dual firing modes, including both draw-activation and a fire button. Rest assured, even those skeptical of new technologies will find the Smok Novo Pro just as user-friendly as its predecessor.
The Smok Novo Pro features 30-watt power, providing flexibility to use both high-VG and low-nicotine vape juices. Its standard 0.6ohm pod is ideal for this purpose, while its draw-activated function allows for long-lasting use with a 1300mAh battery. This kit is the go-to choice for adult vapers seeking dense flavor and vapor.
